Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.68,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.73,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,應該是隊伍全滅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.43,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.08,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,只有自己一個人活了下來…
